# SHELL SHORTCUTS
C-t = Paste selected files and directories on to the command line
C-r = Paste selected command from history on to the command line
Alt-c = cd to the selected directory

# FUZZY BASH COMPLETION
COMMAND [DIRECTORY/] [FUZZY PATTERN]**<TAB>

cd ~/** <tab> = select directory under $HOME directory
vim ../**<tab> = select file under parent direct and open in vim


